msgid "# Test-CauSetup"
msgstr "# Test-CauSetup"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid ""
"Tests whether a cluster is properly set up to apply software updates using "
"CAU."
msgstr "用于测试集群是否已正确配置，以便使用CAU（Cluster Application Update）机制来应用软件更新。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 描述"

msgid ""
"The `Test-CauSetup` cmdlet tests whether a failover cluster is properly set up to apply software\n"
"updates using Cluster-Aware Updating (CAU). The cmdlet performs a Best Practices Analyzer (BPA) scan\n"
"of the failover cluster and network environment by invoking the ClusterAwareUpdating BPA model that\n"
"is installed with CAU. To view the results of a BPA scan that is performed by `Test-CauSetup`,\n"
"including possible problems and resolution steps, run the `Get-BpaResult` cmdlet."
msgstr ""
"`Test-CauSetup` 这个 cmdlet 用于检测故障转移集群是否已正确配置为使用 Cluster-Aware Updating (CAU) "
"来应用软件更新。该 cmdlet 通过调用随 CAU 安装的 ClusterAwareUpdating BPA "
"模型，对故障转移集群和网络环境进行最佳实践分析（Best Practices Analyzer, BPA）扫描。要查看由 `Test-CauSetup`"
" 执行的 BPA 扫描结果（包括可能存在的问题及解决方法），请运行 `Get-BpaResult` cmdlet。"

msgid ""
"You must run the `Test-CauSetup` cmdlet with local administrative "
"credentials."
msgstr "你必须使用本地管理员凭据来运行 `Test-CauSetup` cmdlet。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid ""
"### Example 1: Test whether the specified failover cluster is set up for CAU"
msgstr "### 示例 1：测试指定的故障转移集群是否已设置为支持 CAU（Continuous Availability Update）"

msgid ""
"This example tests whether the failover cluster named CONTOSO-FC1 is "
"properly set up for CAU."
msgstr "这个示例用于测试名为 CONTOSO-FC1 的故障转移集群是否已正确配置以支持 CAU（Content Access Unified）。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the cluster on which to test for proper setup. This parameter is only required\n"
"when this cmdlet isn't run on a failover cluster node, or this cmdlet is used to reference a\n"
"failover cluster different from where the cmdlet is run."
msgstr ""
"指定用于测试是否设置正确的集群名称。只有当此 cmdlet 不在故障转移集群节点上运行，或者用于引用与执行该 cmdlet "
"的位置不同的故障转移集群时，才需要这个参数。"

msgid "Specifies the administrative credentials for the target cluster."
msgstr "指定目标集群的管理凭据。"

